data.description: Don't miss out on this BEAUTIFULLY UPDATED 5 bedroom /3.5 bathroom home near the popular NW Peoria area! This home has been completely remodeled on the first floor including new flooring, new baseboards, gorgeous new kitchen with a large kitchen island, quartz countertops, new cabinets, and stainless steel Bosch appliances. This spacious home includes a mother in law suite on the first level with a remodeled bathroom and walk in closet. The first floor also includes a living room, dining area, and additional space off the kitchen that can be a second living area or dining space. There is also a home gym that could be a separate den/office space. The grand staircase with new balusters leads to 3 bedrooms upstairs, a large loft and the primary suite with custom closet shelving. The primary bedroom also has a private balcony where you can enjoy a cup of coffee or the amazing Arizona sunsets. The beauty continues to the outside of the home with new paint, new black trim windows in the front of the house, and new pavers. This neighborhood is perfect for enjoying the outdoors with playgrounds, tennis courts, basketball courts, and easy access to the best shopping, restaurants, hiking trails and highways in NW Peoria.
